4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge in cybersecurity. This 16-week program includes 3 live online classes per week, with a maximum class size of 16 participants. Students will develop foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration while focusing on cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. The bootcamp covers data loss prevention strategies and compliance with international standards such as ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, students receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. The course is available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop